Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么请您在回收同意书上签名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要和米拉贝尔离别什么的 会变的寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这孩子是小熊小阿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么关于米拉贝尔的回收
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}持有者的您有三个方案可选择
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一是 重新购买的折扣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二是 旧换新来得到定价的三成现金回馈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三是 植入新的OS在米拉贝尔的身体中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是说 换上新的人格继续使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}烦请您植入新的OS了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个… 人格和记忆都会消失喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 以前就是这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前就是 是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:01:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使更换了灵魂我也依然把她当作同一个人对待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.61,0:01:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更换了OS之后的吉芙提尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有没有可能在某种情况下恢复了以前的记忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有呢 从来没有先例
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么可能有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到处瞎转悠就是为了问这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才受不了外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉 满还是一如既往的咄咄逼人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉芙提尔的这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和人类丧失记忆是完全不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}内在被完全替换成全新的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经是不同的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完完全全的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这点上可不要搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以就可以认为无可奈何而果断接受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让人空有期望白白等待才更痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 我也能够理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在来这里之前也曾经想过相同的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以必须想办法让自己去接受这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这也是没有办法的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天第三终端服务派遣的执行者会到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们负责的所有者和回收对象听说躲起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有情报说他们潜伏在我们的负责区域内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以就派人来搜索了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然提出这个要求是在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是希望你们可以去支持她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们就是司和艾拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是第三终端服务的安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说回来 安迪的搭档呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出差要执行者一个人去才是基本政策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一终端服务不是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没出差过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特地派两个人出来效率很低不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在出差地会准备像你们这样的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不会有什么困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是如果艾拉去出差的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我肯定也会跟去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出差什么的我一个人也是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错误 没有听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们两个真是奇怪的组合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奥利维拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的知心好友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2}那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绘瑠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在摸哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想到你居然会反击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是吓到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明以前不管摸多久都不会反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过这样也有这样的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说…两位是认识的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们可是一同度过了青春时代的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:05:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们不是第一次见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绘瑠小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉你跟我朋友长得太像了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不小心认错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还真是冒失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一终端服务这边的人都好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们能就此放弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请在这里签字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜托 放过他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想离开德瑞克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那至少到期限为止让我和他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一周左右的话没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们又会逃跑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}德瑞克！ 德瑞克！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}托你们的福 回收的进程比计划快了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？ 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有必要那么强硬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样的话 和持有者引发矛盾也不足为奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}销毁回忆是我们的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪并没有错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倒不如说终端服务一般都是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有我们不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还要照顾持有者和回收对象的心理感受什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说到底这还是香月三年前开始使用的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就因为这个课长还经常被总部叫过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为经费花得太多被发牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道你在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我刚才去找康孝先生请教了一下关于今天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也想参与你请教的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 那下次就和艾拉聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的长得一模一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 今天就这样 再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才是安迪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前的事想道个歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就打电话给她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后就完全被喜欢上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受欢迎的女性真不好过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说 听你们对话好像你之前就认识安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们以前是邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她当时叫奥莉维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当时？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这真的是安迪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感觉给人印象不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奥莉维亚在几年前被回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道是…更换了OS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看啊 终端服务不是总说要削减经费吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以本来应该被销毁的奥莉维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就被重新利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪还有身为奥莉维亚那时候的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想到还能以这种形式再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然还能揉到那胸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奥莉维亚的 虽然现在是安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前可是经常让我揉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正确的说是我强行去揉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}这人已经没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那已经不是奥莉维亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绘瑠小姐已经不在意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种事不值得在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概是这样的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}点心送到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 谁送的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三终端服务的课长送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 沏茶麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}几天前来的安迪干活真是利落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给人一种「刷刷」地搞定工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「嗖」地就回来了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呜哇 这是在说我们不中用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 并不是那个意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这可难说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不小心和安迪说了我老家嘉年华的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后她非要我带她去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但那个嘉年华是今晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以司司 拜托和我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们两个人好好玩一下不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为那里全是和奥莉维亚在一起的回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和安迪一起去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太折磨人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}毕竟长得一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绘瑠小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司～ 跟我一起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就当作帮我一个忙 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8\fs39}呃 不 等等 啊啊 别抱这么紧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那两个人在偷偷摸摸干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你真的很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连搭档都不告诉肯定有问题不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没有特别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你很在意对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…只是举例而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}带安迪去嘉年华的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以此为契机奥莉维亚的记忆可能会回来一些些… 有可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在思考着艾拉拉的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:13:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论我说什么你都不会那么简单就认同的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以说没关系 司司就尽情的利用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}利用是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚一起去吧 然后在那边用自己的双眼去确认就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用勉强也没关系喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是司的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}顺带一提 安迪也会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有 绘瑠小姐也会跟着去唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 那就这样决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后还会放烟火 很热闹的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我从来都没实际看过烟火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没看过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}声音很大 你一定会吓一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把耳朵塞起来比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 不 不用塞起来也没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 所以说没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘿 还真多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉超可爱 超可爱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总感觉好兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很少有机会来这种地方呢 成为绘瑠的朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就到处逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司… 司！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都只有我和绘瑠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也应该帮艾拉照几张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪 我们喝点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊 有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 要看吗 就像好姐妹一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 要不艾拉也照一张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错误 没有听清楚 请再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那个…拍张照…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错误
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拍照…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错误
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您 您心情不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们两个 来看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}水母果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姑且也算是这个嘉年华的名产果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无法想象什么味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么嘛 喝喝看不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 安迪还是别喝比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯～ 真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然是第一次喝 但味道还不赖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 是吗 还不赖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯～ 绘瑠不敢喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛…嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 那个… 那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去吧 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来吧 艾拉也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小心点别走散啰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我… 又不是小孩子了 才不会走散…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 这个你也来喝喝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…但是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走散了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可恶 大叔再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪好像很快乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}逛了不少地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:17:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么样 你觉得她的记忆有恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明年肯定不会再来这嘉年华了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作为替代 我会和安迪一起去别的地方玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想安迪和奥利维亚共享记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而是希望创造出新的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不这样的话 无论是对安迪还是奥利维亚都很失敬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绘瑠小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你今天陪我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多亏了你 我感觉甩掉了包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不甩掉…不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 小司 能创造回忆的只有当下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只能在这当下这须臾间去创造
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当下这须臾间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 艾拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 难道是走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}振作起来啊 男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 让你一个人在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}声音真的很大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安迪的记忆没有恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是不是让司很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}希望你能够说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想让司因为和我搭档而承受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胸膛都要裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也想要一直做艾拉的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么要坚持到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还问为什么 那种事肯定是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为 我喜欢艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为 我喜欢艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说出口了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为 为什么啊！！！！！
